The '''Alternative Technology Association''' (ATA), established in 1980, is an  independent [[Australia]]n member-based organisation for the promotion and support of [[alternative technology]], spreading awareness and practical knowledge of its application.

It is the publisher of ''[[Renew Magazine]]''.

Its headquarters are [[Melbourne]].
http://www.ata.org.au/

